<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>{include file ='library/admin_html_head.lbi'}</head>

<body class="iframe_body">
	<div class="warpper">
    	<div class="title">{$ur_here}</div>
        <div class="content">
        	<div class="tabs_info">
            	<ul>
                	<li class="curr"><a href="javascript:;">角色介绍</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">会员来源</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">商家入驻</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">购物流程</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">订单售后</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">用户提现</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">商家结算</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">分销设置</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flexilist">
                <div class="common-content">
                    <div class="mian-info operationFlow">
                        <div class="switch_info of_tabmian_one">
                        	<div class="of_item">
                            	<div class="tit">
                                	<i class="icon of-icon-admin"></i>
                                    <h2>平台运营者</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="con">
                                	<p>1、设置商城基本信息设置</p>
                                    <p>2、设置短信，邮件支付方式和商城基础数据维护</p>
                                    <p>3、商城首页，专题页可视化装修</p>
                                    <p>4、商城店铺，会员管理以及促销活动管理</p>
                                    <p>5、门店管理</p>
                                    <p>6、客服</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="of_item">
                            	<div class="tit">
                                	<i class="icon of-icon-store"></i>
                                    <h2>店铺管理员</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="con">
                                	<p>1、设置店铺信息</p>
                                    <p>2、发布店铺商品，以及商品库管理</p>
                                    <p>3、装修自己的店铺以及专题</p>
                                    <p>4、处理订单以及退换货</p>
                                    <p>5、设置自己的促销活动</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="of_item">
                            	<div class="tit">
                                	<i class="icon of-icon-finance"></i>
                                    <h2>财务管理员</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="con">
                                	<p>1、客户统计</p>
                                    <p>2、订单统计</p>
                                    <p>3、销售明细访问购买率</p>
                                    <p>4、商家佣金结算</p>
                                    <p>5、资金管理</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="of_item">
                            	<div class="tit">
                                	<i class="icon of-icon-web"></i>
                                    <h2>网站管理员</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="con">
                                	<p>1、处理订单</p>
                                    <p>2、处理退换货订单</p>
                                    <p>3、发布以及维护商品及商品库</p>
                                    <p>4、管理用户评论以及留言</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="of_item">
                            	<div class="tit">
                                	<i class="icon of-icon-consumption"></i>
                                    <h2>消费者</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="con">
                                	<p>1、浏览平台</p>
                                    <p>2、注册会员账号</p>
                                    <p>3、购物、下单支付</p>
                                    <p>4、协助平台监督商家商品（商品举报）</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>会员来源</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>消费者可以通过平台的PC端、APP端、微商城等前台入口申请账号；平台可自行添加会员信息、调整资金等。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_1.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>商家入驻</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>商家在进行入驻申请时需要先成为平台的会员，然后填写入驻信息、等待平台审核；平台可自行添加自营店铺、通过商家后台统筹管理。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        	<div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_2.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>购物流程</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>平台购物模式多样，针对不同购物模式，商家分别在不同时间段进行发货操作。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        	<div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_3.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>订单售后</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>商家进行售后操作需要通过平台开放的退换货权限，否则商家所有的售后退款都由平台方执行。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_4.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>用户提现</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>为用户提现的操作由平台线下进行，平台可以通过会员申请提现时填写的备注信息或绑定的银行卡，进行转账操作，转账完成即提现成功。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        	<div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_5.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                            <div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>商家结算</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>平台可设置商家的结算日期和结算比例，商家可通过自己的后台查看自己能分到的佣金比例，方便对账。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_6.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="switch_info" style="display:none;">
                        	<div class="explanation">
                                <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>分销</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="{$lang.fold_tips}"></span></div>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>免费版的大商创系统不具备分销功能的设置，需购买大商创微商城的分销功能才能开展分销传播。</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="img"><img src="images/guide/of_img_7.png" /></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
		</div>
	</div>
	{include file ='library/pagefooter.lbi'}
</body>
</html>
